Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.49,0:00:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.57,0:00:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你在這種地方幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  其實有件事情不得不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起私奔吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？私奔是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然提出這種要求我也知道你很混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我需要次郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  只是會有點睏而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家是無法違逆主人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼一回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯覺嗎次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有股土豆燉肉的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有一種類似女孩子的味道

